HOLLOW out tomatoes, leaving a 1/4-inch wall around sides and bottom. Place in 9-inch-round cake pan to prevent tipping. COMBINE bread crumbs, cheese and butter in small bowl; sprinkle mixture evenly on top of each tomato. COMBINE hot Macaroni and Cheese, bacon and onion in medium bowl; fill tomatoes with mixture. BAKE in preheated 350 degrees F. oven for 15 to 20 minutes or until cheese is melted.